reviews.text:
makgeolli tasting menu is a must try. 
the pork leg tastes good and authentic with great texture. 
for korean, pancake and makgeolli is perfect match so make sure you order one.
Really hip spot, great bites

Dinner meal sets terrible:
- soggy seafood pancake
- no flavour boiled pork belly
- microwaved pumpkin rice

HKD$380 for 2 people - still hungry afterward!
Tried new things n good

Great Korean restaurant, food was absolutely delicious. We ordered pork belly and seafood pancake. The pork belly was larger than expected while the seafood pancake was freshly prepared and arrived hot! This restaurant has a lot of choices for rice wines (makgeolli). The service was also amazing, the servers were friendly and helpful overall.
